with an American man

31:36.900 --> 31:39.350
and an eastern
European woman?

31:39.352 --> 31:42.036
Well, could it have been
Frankie's parents?

31:42.038 --> 31:43.011
She said she was petite.

31:43.036 --> 31:45.386
Garcia, any idea how tall
