autopsy records now.

31:48.545 --> 31:49.977
Nadia was 5'8".

31:49.979 --> 31:52.129
No, it wasn't her.

31:52.131 --> 31:54.932
But there's gotta be
a connection here somewhere.

31:54.934 --> 31:57.635
Nadia's Romanian.
Lida Taffert is Polish.

31:57.637 --> 31:59.587
Then there's a third woman
from 15 years ago

31:59.589 --> 32:01.923
who's eastern European.
Maybe she's the unsub's mother.

32:01.925 --> 32:03.391
Well, that first call
to the Clayvins

32:03.393 --> 32:06.561
came around the one-year
anniversary of Nadia's death.

32:07.729 --> 32:11.432
Maybe the unsub's mother
committed suicide as well.

32:14.686 --> 32:17.521
