we need to figure out

32:17.523 --> 32:20.358
who the mystery woman is.

32:48.086 --> 32:50.554
There's a GPS tracking app
on Malcolm's cell phone.

32:50.556 --> 32:53.608
The unsub could have easily located
the Tafferts at the motel through that.

32:54.760 --> 32:55.759
Go ahead, Garcia.

32:55.761 --> 32:57.311
I have got a list
of Easter European women

32:57.313 --> 32:58.590
around the Memphis area

32:58.615 --> 33:00.816
who committed suicide
within the last 4 decades.

33:00.817 --> 33:03.117
It's a short list. The most
relevant name is Olga Milworth,

33:03.119 --> 33:05.102
who was from Romania.

33:05.104 --> 33:06.203
Like Nadia Clayvin was.

33:06.205 --> 33:07.722
Yeah. She was married
to an American

33:07.724 --> 33:10.157
named Charles Milworth,
and 19 yea ago

33:10.159 --> 33:12.076
she tried to kill herself
and her son.

33:12.078 --> 33:14.211
Get this--her son survived.

33:15.113 --> 33:16.247
What's his name?

33:16.249 --> 33:17.614
His name's Daniel Milworth,

33:17.616 --> 33:20.718
and he was incarcerated
in Arizona for 11 years

33:20.720 --> 33:23.387
in a psychiatric hospital
for the criminally insane

33:23.389 --> 33:26.223
because he kidnapped
and tortured a prostitute.

33:26.225 --> 33:27.745
That would explain
his dormancy period.

33:27.750 --> 33:29.061
Garcia, where is he now?

33:29.062 --> 33:30.594
Uh, well,
once he was released,

33:30.596 --> 33:32.430
it appears he vanished.

33:32.432 --> 33:33.848
There's no record
of him anywhere.

33:33.850 --> 33:36.150
I'm gonna take a guess
he changed his identity.

33:51.583 --> 33:53.117
You know this man?

33:53.119 --> 33:54.785
If you took away
the beard and the glasses,

33:54.787 --> 33:58.673
he looks like Andy's
computer science teacher at school.

33:58.675 --> 34:01.959
Um...Burt Solomon.

34:01.961 --> 34:04.161
Was Andy close to him?

34:04.163 --> 34:05.463
He was one of his favorites.

34:05.465 --> 34:09.166
I guess he lets the kids
play video games in class.

34:09.168 --> 34:12.687
That could be how
Andy was lured out.

34:19.010 --> 34:21.862
And why Lida stopped
for someone.

34:28.203 --> 34:30.353
Are you saying
Burt Solomon did this?

34:30.356 --> 34:31.661
We can't say for sure,

34:31.686 --> 34:32.741
but we definitely
need to talk to him.

34:32.742 --> 34:35.242
As soon as we know anything,
you'll be the first to know.

34:35.244 --> 34:37.962
Garcia, I need an address
for Burt Solomon.

34:37.964 --> 34:39.580
He's a teacher
at Andy Taffert's school

34:54.096 --> 34:55.096
Hello.

34:55.098 --> 34:57.063
Did you see what I did?

34:57.065 --> 34:58.899
Did you see it?

35:00.068 --> 35:02.219
What the hell
did you do to her?

35:02.221 --> 35:03.604
Did you kill Lida?!

35:03.606 --> 35:05.773
Did you?!

35:21.583 --> 35:24.834
Burt Solomon's been teaching
at Andy's school for two years.

35:24.836 --> 35:27.504
It fits the timeline.
He's gotta be our unsub.

35:27.506 --> 35:29.672
Burt Solomon,
aka Daniel Milworth,

35:29.674 --> 35:31.591
probably
bought a fake I.D.

35:31.593 --> 35:34.094
and even fake
teaching credentials.

35:34.096 --> 35:35.712
What have you got,
Garcia?

35:35.714 --> 35:37.464
I've got more information
on Daniel Milworth.

35:37.466 --> 35:39.099
According to prison
psychiatric records,

35:39.101 --> 35:41.351
his mom was a Romanian
mail order bride.

35:41.353 --> 35:43.636
His dad made her perform

35:43.638 --> 35:45.555
demeaning sex acts
with prostitutes

35:45.557 --> 35:48.341
and then he forced young
Daniel to watch.

35:48.343 --> 35:50.176
No!

35:50.178 --> 35:52.178
Stop! Stop!

35:53.482 --> 35:55.281
Aah!

35:55.283 --> 35:57.634
If the mother spoke
poor English and was unskilled,

35:57.636 --> 36:00.019
