how did the mother die?

36:05.160 --> 36:08.294
Uh, she drive a car
into a lake.

36:20.474 --> 36:24.511
Daniel managed to break out
a window and escape.

36:24.513 --> 36:26.596
Any idea
how Daniel Milworth

36:26.598 --> 36:28.314
crossed paths
with the Clayvins?

36:28.316 --> 36:30.886
Yeah. He volunteered as a
teacher's aide while he was in college,

36:30.887 --> 36:32.538
and one of the schools
he happened to work at

36:32.539 --> 36:34.038
was Frankie's.

36:34.489 --> 36:36.940
Seeing the American father/
immigrant mother dynamic

36:36.942 --> 36:38.975
must have amplified his negative
feelings about his own family,

36:38.977 --> 36:41.177
especially after Nadia Clayvin
committed suicide.

36:41.179 --> 36:43.396
And after a stint in prison,
he saw the same dynamic again

36:43.398 --> 36:45.031
in Andy Taffert's parents.

36:45.033 --> 36:47.733
But Lida Taffert didn't
try to commit suicide.

36:47.735 --> 36:49.786
No, she didn't have to.

36:49.788 --> 36:52.122
He'd killed once already
and he saw the similarity

36:52.124 --> 36:54.124
